        "body": "#### What is it?\r\n- [ ] Bugfix (user facing)\r\n- [ ] Feature (user facing)\r\n- [x] Codebase improvement (dev facing)\r\n- [ ] Meta improvement to the project (dev facing)\r\n\r\n#### Description of the changes in your PR\r\n- Update Jsoup 1.16.1 -> 1.16.2 ([changelog](https://jsoup.org/news/release-1.16.2))\r\n- Update OkHttp 4.11.0 -> 4.12.0 ([changelog](https://square.github.io/okhttp/changelogs/changelog_4x/#version-4120))\r\n- Update ACRA 5.10.1 -> 5.11.3 ([changelog](https://github.com/ACRA/acra/releases))\r\n- Update RxJava 3.1.6 -> 3.1.8 ([changelog](https://github.com/ReactiveX/RxJava/releases))\r\n- Update Prettytime 5.0.6.Final -> 5.0.7.Final ([changelog](https://github.com/ocpsoft/prettytime/compare/5.0.6.Final...5.0.7.Final))\r\n- Update Mockito 4.0.0 -> 5.6.0 ([changelog](https://github.com/mockito/mockito/releases))\r\n- Update AssertJ 3.23.1 -> 3.24.2 ([changelog](https://github.com/assertj/assertj/releases))\r\n- Update Kotlin 1.8.22 -> 1.9.10 ([changelog](https://kotlinlang.org/docs/whatsnew19.html))\r\n- Update AGP 8.1.1 -> 8.1.2 ([changelog](https://developer.android.com/studio/releases/fixed-bugs/studio/2022.3.1#android-studio-giraffe-|-2022.3.1-patch-2))\r\n\r\n#### APK testing\r\nThe APK can be found by going to the \"Checks\" tab below the title. On the left pane, click on \"CI\", scroll down to \"artifacts\" and click \"app\" to download the zip file which contains the debug APK of this PR. You can find more info and a video demonstration [on this wiki page](https://github.com/TeamNewPipe/NewPipe/wiki/Download-APK-for-PR).\r\n\r\n#### Due diligence\r\n- [x] I read the [contribution guidelines](https://github.com/TeamNewPipe/NewPipe/blob/HEAD/.github/CONTRIBUTING.md).\r\n",
