        "body": "#### What is it?\r\n- [ ] Bugfix (user facing)\r\n- [ ] Feature (user facing)\r\n- [x] Codebase improvement (dev facing)\r\n- [ ] Meta improvement to the project (dev facing)\r\n\r\n#### Description of the changes in your PR\r\n- Update AppCompat 1.5.1 -> 1.6.1 ([changelog](https://developer.android.com/jetpack/androidx/releases/appcompat))\r\n- Update Core 1.10.0 -> 1.12.0 ([changelog](https://developer.android.com/jetpack/androidx/releases/core#1.12.0))\r\n- Update Fragment 1.4.1 -> 1.6.1 ([changelog](https://developer.android.com/jetpack/androidx/releases/fragment#1.6.1))\r\n- Update Lifecycle 2.5.1 -> 2.6.2 ([changelog](https://developer.android.com/jetpack/androidx/releases/lifecycle))\r\n- Update Preference 1.2.0 -> 1.2.1 ([changelog](https://developer.android.com/jetpack/androidx/releases/preference#1.2.1))\r\n- Update RecyclerView 1.2.1 -> 1.3.2 ([changelog](https://developer.android.com/jetpack/androidx/releases/recyclerview))\r\n- Update ViewPager2 1.1.0-beta1 -> 1.1.0-beta2 ([changelog](https://developer.android.com/jetpack/androidx/releases/viewpager2#1.1.0-beta02))\r\n- Update WorkManager 2.7.1 -> 2.8.1 ([changelog](https://developer.android.com/jetpack/androidx/releases/work#2.8.1))\r\n- Update `compileSdk` to 34\r\n- Use new compatibility methods in `BundleCompat` and `IntentCompat` to fix some deprecations\r\n\r\n#### APK testing\r\nThe APK can be found by going to the \"Checks\" tab below the title. On the left pane, click on \"CI\", scroll down to \"artifacts\" and click \"app\" to download the zip file which contains the debug APK of this PR.\r\n\r\n#### Due diligence\r\n- [x] I read the [contribution guidelines](https://github.com/TeamNewPipe/NewPipe/blob/HEAD/.github/CONTRIBUTING.md).\r\n",
