        "body": "\r\n#### What is it?\r\n- [ ] Bugfix (user facing)\r\n- [x] Feature (user facing)\r\n- [ ] Codebase improvement (dev facing)\r\n- [ ] Meta improvement to the project (dev facing)\r\n\r\n#### Description of the changes in your PR\r\n- pauses video player when internet disconnects with ERROR_CODE_IO_NETWORK_CONNECTION_FAILED\r\n- disables error notification setting isCatchableException = true\r\n- adds toast method to error util\r\n- modifies play() to prepare() video if video is not prepared\r\n\r\n#### Before/After Screenshots/Screen Record\r\n- Before: \r\n![NewPipeError](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/115518657/198860240-96410bf5-cd10-455b-9f31-86cec2dc34a6.png)\r\n\r\n![NewPipeErrorMessage](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/115518657/198859962-3937c34c-d355-484f-9eb6-b9a9ffb45f9d.png)\r\n\r\n- After: \r\n![NewPipeNetworkToast](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/115518657/198859966-6249837a-623c-49b2-92be-a89714143605.png)\r\n\r\n#### Fixes the following issue(s)\r\n- Fixes #8898\r\n\r\n\r\n#### APK testing\r\nThe APK can be found by going to the \"Checks\" tab below the title. On the left pane, click on \"CI\", scroll down to \"artifacts\" and click \"app\" to download the zip file which contains the debug APK of this PR.\r\n\r\n#### Due diligence\r\n- [x] I read the [contribution guidelines](https://github.com/TeamNewPipe/NewPipe/blob/HEAD/.github/CONTRIBUTING.md).\r\n",
